name: Sweet Lucy
description:
I ate a candy
Sweet, sweet candy

My feet are numb
My wings are cold

O'er the fields of cloud I fly
Among the yellow grass, I lay
Gazing into my empty mind

I watch the world turned cellophane
When smog and haze should turn in vain

I wait
...And I wait
And I wait...

Time is ticking slow
And my feelings blow
...Sweet, sweet lullaby
